---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import GeneralHero from "@/components/HeroSections/GeneralHero.astro"
---

<Layout>
    <GeneralHero title="Privacy Policy"/>
    <section
    id="ori-team-details"
    class="ori-team-details-section position-relative"
>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="ori-team-details-content">
            <div class="ori-team-personal-info-wrapper">
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>Privacy Policy</h3>
                    <h2 class="date">Last Updated: 24 DEC, 2024</h2>
                    <p>
                        Welcome to Devliqly! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal
                        information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
                        use, and protect your personal information when you use our services.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
                    <p>
                        We collect various types of information to provide and improve our services, including:
                        <p class="list">
                            &bull; Personal identification details such as name, email address, phone number, etc.
                            <br />
                            &bull; Payment information for processing transactions.
                            <br />
                            &bull; Project details and feedback you provide during the project.
                            <br />
                            &bull; Technical data such as browser type, IP address, and usage data for analytics purposes.
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                    <p>
                        We use the information we collect for various purposes, including:
                        <p class="list">
                            &bull; To provide, maintain, and improve our services.
                            <br />
                            &bull; To communicate with you, including project updates, service-related information, and promotional offers (if opted-in).
                            <br />
                            &bull; To process payments and manage transactions.
                            <br />
                            &bull; To analyze usage trends and improve the user experience.
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>3. Sharing Your Information</h3>
                    <p>
                        We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your
                        information in the following situations:
                        <p class="list">
                            &bull; With trusted third-party service providers who assist us in delivering services (e.g., payment processors).
                            <br />
                            &bull; If required by law, to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights and safety.
                            <br />
                            &bull; In the event of a business transfer, such as a merger, acquisition, or asset sale.
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>4. Data Security</h3>
                    <p>
                        We use a variety of security measures, including encryption and secure protocols, to protect your
                        personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration. However, no method of
                        transmission or electronic storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
                    <p>
                        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your experience and collect data on how
                        you interact with our services. You can control cookie settings through your browser settings, but
                        disabling cookies may impact the functionality of our services.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>6. Your Data Protection Rights</h3>
                    <p>
                        Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal data:
                        <p class="list">
                            &bull; The right to access the personal information we hold about you.
                            <br />
                            &bull; The right to correct or update any incorrect information.
                            <br />
                            &bull; The right to request the deletion of your personal data.
                            <br />
                            &bull; The right to object to or restrict the processing of your personal data.
                            <br />
                        </p>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>7. Data Retention</h3>
                    <p>
                        We will retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this
                        Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>8. Third-Party Links</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our services may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the
                        privacy practices of such third-party sites, and we encourage you to read their privacy policies before
                        interacting with them.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>9. Children's Privacy</h3>
                    <p>
                        Our services are not intended for individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect or
                        solicit personal information from children under 18. If we learn that we have collected personal
                        information from a child under 18, we will take steps to delete that information.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>10. Changes to this Privacy Policy</h3>
                    <p>
                        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an
                        updated "Last Updated" date. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically to stay informed about
                        how we are protecting your information.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="ori-team-personal-info pera-content">
                    <h3>11. Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>
                        If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your personal
                        information, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact.devliqly@gmail.com"><b>contact.devliqly@gmail.com</b></a>. 
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="line_animation">
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
        <div class="line_area"></div>
    </div>
</section>

    
</Layout>
<style>
    .date {
      font-size: 20px;
      padding-top: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .list{
      padding-top: 10px;
      margin-left: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      /* margin-bottom: 0; */
    }
   
  </style>